{"tha-ap318:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap318:0.2":"Arakkhadayakavagga ","tha-ap318:0.3":"6 Asanasanthavikattheraapadana ","tha-ap318:1.1":"“Cetiyam uttamam nama, ","tha-ap318:1.2":"sikhino lokabandhuno; ","tha-ap318:1.3":"Aranne irine vane, ","tha-ap318:1.4":"andhahindamaham tada. ","tha-ap318:2.1":"Pavana nikkhamantena, ","tha-ap318:2.2":"dittham sihasanam maya; ","tha-ap318:2.3":"Ekamsam anjalim katva, ","tha-ap318:2.4":"santhavim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap318:3.1":"Divasabhagam thavitvana, ","tha-ap318:3.2":"buddham lokagganayakam; ","tha-ap318:3.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap318:3.4":"imam vacam udirayim. ","tha-ap318:4.1":"‘Namo te purisajanna, ","tha-ap318:4.2":"namo te purisuttama; ","tha-ap318:4.3":"Sabbannusi mahavira, ","tha-ap318:4.4":"lokajettha narasabha’. ","tha-ap318:5.1":"Abhitthavitva sikhinam, ","tha-ap318:5.2":"nimittakaranenaham; ","tha-ap318:5.3":"Asanam abhivadetva, ","tha-ap318:5.4":"pakkamim uttaramukho. ","tha-ap318:6.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap318:6.2":"yam thavim vadatam varam; ","tha-ap318:6.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap318:6.4":"thomanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap318:7.1":"Sattavise ito kappe, ","tha-ap318:7.2":"atula satta asu te; ","tha-ap318:7.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap318:7.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap318:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap318:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap318:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap318:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma asanasanthaviko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap318:10.1":"Asanasanthavikattherassapadanam chattham. "}